 History:
 --------

 version 1.2 (07.05.2020) done by JOTD:
 - added joypad support for pause, weapon switch, etc...
 - blue/second button jumps if CUSTOM2 is set
 - fixed more sountracker replay loops (menu music)
 - grouped all trainer option in CUSTOM1 bits
 
 version 1.1 (02.11.2017) done by StingRay:
 - RawDIC imager
 - Bplcon0 color bit fixes
 - keyboard routine rewritten
 - trainer options added
 - source code included
 - readme reworked
 - new install script

 version 1.0 (1998) done by Harry:
 - initial version

 Joypad controls:
 
 - blue/second button: jumps (if option is selected)
 - play: pause/unpause (like P key)
 - green: call merchant (like H key)
 - yellow: switch weapon (like space key)
 - fwd+bwd: lose life (like ESC key)
 - yellow+fwd+bwd: give up play (like DEL key)
 - green+yellow+fwd+bwd: quit to workbench
 
 Contact:
 --------
 If you have problems with this installation please try and get a newer
 version of this package from the WHDLoad WWW-Page. If that doesn't help try
 some Tooltypes like NOCACHE, NOAUTOVEC, EXPCHIP, NOMMU, PAL or NTSC. If
 that also fails, please inform the author via the Bug-Report-Form which
 can be accessed on the WHDLoad WWW-Page or create a mantis issue directly
 at http://mantis.whdload.de

 For the full WHDLoad package, other installs and updates refer to:
	http://www.whdload.de/
 or	aminet:dev/misc/whdload#?
 and	aminet:game/patch/

